•—ظRarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2024-02-23-twin0235.mdظ@fb0cf32e9e33e2fec4b3eeb3950d0f3851ed3f7bdbe44e5aad846a176dbf218e¹This Week in Nushell #235‘§Nushellع
÷fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11938] removed unused dependencies
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11909] fixed the 
``debug info``
 command to populate process information accurately, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11906] enabled 
``last``
 to work with ranges
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11878] updated to the latest versions of reedline and rusqlite
.
devyn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11937] replaced 
``debug_assert!``
 with 
``assert!``
 in signature checks and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11924] added support for closures as arguments to the 
``zip``
 command
.
ayax79 improved stability with contributions to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11935] handle configuration panics
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11860] wrap the REPL in a catch_unwind to restart it upon a panic
.
WindSoilder made 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11914] stderr output improvements for failed external commands
 and ensured certain commands like 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11886] open, rm, and cp don't perform globbing
 when inputs are variables or string interpolations.
dmatos2012 focused on user experience with a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11908] fix for date formatting
 according to the user's locale.
dannou812 added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11904] new tests and fixes for the 
``move``
 command
, making it more robust.
sholderbach embarked on a cleanup mission with 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11903] removal of unused implementations and error variants
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11876] updating the 
``roxmltree``
 dependency
.
lpnh 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11889] corrected keybinding names and improved formatting
 in the default Nushell configuration.
IanManske made internal improvements to how 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11885] ``Value``
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11810] ``Record``
 are converted.
kit494way improved some user commands by 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11877] splitting 
``commandline``
 into subcommands
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11871] fixing a panic in 
``seq date``
.
kubouch optimized the Nushell engine by 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11872] removing an unnecessary state clone
.
yurivict implemented 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11869] FreeBSD compatibility enhancements
.
ysthakur refined error messaging by 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11868] specifying which files were not found in 
``ShellError::FileNotFound``
.
